{"tid":109563,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"真心，點解唔支持林鄭？","createTime":"2017-02-06T05:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T04:11:27.000Z","uid":63841,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c56f68299cf9752dc53484de6bbbe910a785de6","tid":109563,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:03:03.000Z","msg":"當年梁振英一上任已經有上街遊行喇，連<br />\n主流支持泛民左膠都唔鍾意佢，有名你叫啦 ，港獨之父嘛<br />\n<br />\n畀着薯片做特首啲人會唔會咁反政府呀<br />\n<br />\n反而林鄭得喎，佢同梁振英一樣，有嗰種令人反政府嘅凝聚力。<br />\n<br />\n如果薯片做咗特首，香港冇錯係會好和諧，和諧到唔會有反政府嘅勢力抬頭。<br />\n<br />\n真係唔明啲人會支持薯片做特首，佢做特首又唔係唔會唔推嗰啲仆街惡法<br />\n<br />\n佢做特首嘅就真係溫水煮蛙啦"},{"pid":"a34389f3a3c9a0e3bdecbcd0bded53185522ea2f","tid":109563,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:05:36.000Z","msg":"根本香港就需要越大嘅打壓，如果唔係根本就唔會有反抗。"},{"pid":"6f9a31c82742218df87e47b5ba8a1b893903d2e8","tid":109563,"uid":32486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"所以我支持中共"},{"pid":"a71cbc0ba08ca7290bca813d802d1aa0afeab4dd","tid":109563,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"支持林鄭同葉劉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951c649e08aa172cdd33c4d57f723f5ce2abe05b","tid":109563,"uid":27484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:15:50.000Z","msg":"林鄭做 社會撕裂得更嚴重"},{"pid":"a6e9f152f66c82e617f806d47e22340af2c372ea","tid":109563,"uid":20498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"無票...支唔支持有咩分別"},{"pid":"ca51084d8b17cdbbd4a91cb6dc39487db330d30c","tid":109563,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林鄭做 社會撕裂得更嚴重</blockquote><br />\n 社會撕裂， 有乜壞處"},{"pid":"6144368545669b4426f7d57a514e3d87bc7ec814","tid":109563,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無票...支唔支持有咩分別</bloc